text: Caroline Brittan (born 9 March 1959) is a British cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 5 kilometres at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:British female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Great Britain Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
